        </apply>
        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>This TSI applies to 3900 series with Douglas tilt steering column.</para>
                <para>If the turn signal on a 3900 Series vehicle with a Douglas tilt steering column (code 05708) will
                    not cancel after a turn, the following parts and repair information should be used to correct the
                    condition.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
